Package: clir
Type: Package
Title: Command Line Argument Parser for R
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(
        "Brandon Monier", 
        email = "brandon.monier@gmail.com", 
        role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
Description: 
    An argument parser similar to Python's argparse, implemented using pure R 
    and the S7 class system. Provides a flexible and intuitive interface for 
    parsing command-line arguments in R scripts.
